do &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; chaar ( english : two &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; are four ) is a 2010 indian hindi comedy-drama film produced by arindam chaudhuri ( &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; motion pictures ) , directed by habib faisal , and stars rishi kapoor , neetu singh , aditi vasudev and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; krishna in lead roles . the film is about a middle-class school teacher who tries to keep his wife and children happy in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; times and dreams of buying a car . the movie also marks the return of the kapoor pair as a lead couple on the silver screen . although the duo has not acted in a film in over 30 years , they had previously acted in numerous hits during the 1970s . the directorial debut film was also the first live action hindi film to be distributed by disney world cinema . the film was declared a hit by box office india .